00:17:14,915 --> 00:17:16,448
PRETTY SOON, I HAD TO
PUT MY FOOT DOWN

454
00:17:16,548 --> 00:17:18,948
AND BRING AN END TO IT.

455
00:17:19,048 --> 00:17:20,581
YOU BOTH TOOK IT VERY HARD.

456
00:17:20,681 --> 00:17:22,848
I STILL REMEMBER
THE SAD LOOKS ON YOUR FACES.

457
00:17:22,948 --> 00:17:24,248
YOU WERE MISERABLE.

458
00:17:24,348 --> 00:17:26,348
THINGS NEVER CHANGED
AS YOU GREW UP.

459
00:17:26,448 --> 00:17:28,448
YOU STILL SPENT
LONG PERIODS OF TIME

460
00:17:28,548 --> 00:17:31,215
DREAMING ABOUT THAT STRANGE
OTHER WORLD OF YOURS.

461
00:17:31,315 --> 00:17:33,215
YOU NEVER LET ANYONE ELSE
SHARE IN YOUR THOUGHTS

462
00:17:33,315 --> 00:17:34,815
BECAUSE IF YOU DID,

463
00:17:34,915 --> 00:17:37,548
YOU WERE AFRAID
THEY WOULD TAKE THEM AWAY.

464
00:17:37,648 --> 00:17:40,548
THEN ONE DAY IT HAPPENED.
HIROKI WAS GONE FOREVER.

465
00:17:40,648 --> 00:17:42,948
YOU WERE BESIDE YOURSELF
WITH GRIEF.

466
00:17:43,048 --> 00:17:45,115
YOU BECAME
A LOST AND LONELY SOUL.

467
00:17:45,215 --> 00:17:46,515
IT WASN'T NORMAL,

468
00:17:46,615 --> 00:17:49,081
BUT THEN, HIROKI HAD BEEN
YOUR ONLY FRIEND.

469
00:17:49,181 --> 00:17:52,081
I WISH I COULD HAVE
SEEN IT COMING.

470
00:17:52,181 --> 00:17:55,048
I WOULD HAVE TRIED
TO MAKE IT EASIER FOR YOU.

471
00:17:55,148 --> 00:17:58,015
I'VE NEVER SEEN ANYONE
SO SAD IN MY LIFE.

472
00:17:58,115 --> 00:18:01,981
I HAVE TO SAY IT WAS
A VERY DIFFICULT THING TO WATCH.

473
00:18:02,081 --> 00:18:04,081
YOU MAY NOT BE INTERESTED
IN HEARING THIS,

474
00:18:04,181 --> 00:18:06,081
BUT I'D LIKE TO BE
YOUR FRIEND.

475
00:18:06,181 --> 00:18:08,955
IT WOULD BE NICE TO TALK
TO SOMEONE ABOUT MY SON.

476
00:18:09,055 --> 00:18:11,921
DO YOU THINK
THAT WOULD BE ALL RIGHT?

477
00:18:12,021 --> 00:18:14,888
HUH? YOU MUST MISS HIM
EVEN MORE THAN I DO.

478
00:18:14,988 --> 00:18:17,388
UHH!

479
00:18:17,488 --> 00:18:22,788
AHH!

480
00:18:22,888 --> 00:18:24,421
GRR.

481
00:18:24,521 --> 00:18:26,155
GET AWAY FROM THERE,
GRANDPA!

482
00:18:26,255 --> 00:18:30,155
Armadillomon: HE'S NOT LOOKING
TOO NEIGHBORLY TO ME.

483
00:18:34,455 --> 00:18:36,421
Both: BLACK WARGREYMON!

484
00:18:36,521 --> 00:18:39,955
Cody: WOW. DID YOU SEE THAT?
HE PROTECTED GRANDPA.

485
00:18:40,055 --> 00:18:42,921
HA HA HA HA!

486
00:18:43,021 --> 00:18:45,888
OH, NO! YOU!

487
00:18:45,988 --> 00:18:48,888
IT CAN'T BE. NO!

488
00:18:48,988 --> 00:18:51,255
T.K.: THERE MUST BE SOMETHING
MORE TO THIS THAN WE CAN SEE.

489
00:18:51,355 --> 00:18:54,188
HOW COULD I HAVE BEEN
SO BLIND?

490
00:18:54,288 --> 00:18:56,055
I SHOULD HAVE KNOWN.

491
00:18:56,155 --> 00:18:58,455
YOU'RE PERFECTLY RIGHT
ABOUT BEING ALONE.

492
00:18:58,555 --> 00:19:01,221
WE'RE BOTH DOOMED
TO REMAIN THIS WAY FOREVER.

493
00:19:01,321 --> 00:19:03,421
THERE ISN'T ANY OTHER CHOICE.

494
00:19:03,521 --> 00:19:05,188
HE'S CONTROLLING YOU.

495
00:19:05,288 --> 00:19:07,755
THIS CHANGES EVERYTHING.

496
00:19:07,855 --> 00:19:10,395
YOU'RE VERY PERCEPTIVE
FOR SOMEONE SO NARROW-MINDED.

497
00:19:10,495 --> 00:19:12,695
I HAVE TO HARVEST
ALL THE DARK SPORES

498
00:19:12,795 --> 00:19:15,095
IN ORDER FOR ME TO FULFILL
MY DEEPEST DESIRE.

499
00:19:15,195 --> 00:19:17,728
I'VE ALWAYS WANTED TO GO
TO THE DIGITAL WORLD.

500
00:19:17,828 --> 00:19:20,095
HA HA HA HA HA!

501
00:19:20,195 --> 00:19:22,095
HE MUST NOT BE ALLOWED

502
00:19:22,195 --> 00:19:24,461
INTO THE DIGITAL WORLD
EVER AGAIN!

503
00:19:24,561 --> 00:19:26,461
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, AGAIN?

504
00:19:26,561 --> 00:19:28,361
AGAIN? NOBODY EVER
TELLS ME ANYTHING.

505
00:19:28,461 --> 00:19:29,828
YOU ALL RIGHT, BIG GUY?

506
00:19:29,928 --> 00:19:31,961
MY BODY'S NOT GOING TO LAST
MUCH LONGER.

507
00:19:32,061 --> 00:19:33,961
THE IMAGE CREATED
BY THE CONTROL SPIRES

508
00:19:34,061 --> 00:19:35,795
WILL SOON START
TO BREAK UP,

509
00:19:35,895 --> 00:19:39,095
BUT THERE'S STILL SOMETHING
I HAVE TO DO.

510
00:19:39,195 --> 00:19:40,761
SAVE YOUR STRENGTH.

511
00:19:40,861 --> 00:19:44,728
NO. MY STRENGTH IS MY FINAL GIFT
TO YOU, MY FRIENDS.

512
00:19:44,828 --> 00:19:47,128
I WILL SEAL
THE HIGHTON VIEW TERRACE GATE

513
00:19:47,228 --> 00:19:48,895
WITH MY OWN BODY.

514
00:19:48,995 --> 00:19:50,195
DON'T DO IT.

515
00:19:50,295 --> 00:19:51,328
I MUST.

516
00:19:51,428 --> 00:19:56,095
AAH!

517
00:20:03,995 --> 00:20:06,128
HE ALWAYS WANTED TO DO SOMETHING
MEANINGFUL WITH HIS LIFE.

518
00:20:06,228 --> 00:20:08,128
I'D SAY
THIS DEFINITELY QUALIFIES.

519
00:20:08,228 --> 00:20:10,901
BLACK WARGREYMON.

520
00:20:11,001 --> 00:20:14,901
BLACK WARGREYMON!

521
00:20:15,001 --> 00:20:18,401
BLACK WARGREYMON!

522
00:20:18,501 --> 00:20:20,901
