ANOTHER WAY.

523
00:20:21,001 --> 00:20:23,868
OOH! WHAT'S THAT?

524
00:20:23,968 --> 00:20:25,635
AHH.

525
00:20:25,735 --> 00:20:27,635
THANK YOU,
BLACK WARGREYMON.

526
00:20:27,735 --> 00:20:30,868
YOU'RE A TRUE A FRIEND,
AND I'LL NEVER FORGET YOU.

527
00:20:30,968 --> 00:20:32,868
BLACK WARGREYMON
SEALED THE GATE,

528
00:20:32,968 --> 00:20:35,268
BUT WILL THE IMPOSTOR
